title: G5 Looking for 5's Team in order to get end of season rewards.
body:
Howdy, I'm currently a G5 (Solo) and I'm looking for a ranked 5's team in order to gain enough wins in order to get the end of season ward. I mainly play support, though do fill for mid/top if required (Though they aren't my strongest roles).

So if you are looking for a quick fill, feel free to give me a shout.
